36#include "kadm5_locl.h"
37
38__RCSID("$NetBSD: free.c,v 1.2 2017/01/28 21:31:49 christos Exp $");
39
40void
41kadm5_free_key_data(void *server_handle,
42 int16_t *n_key_data,
43 krb5_key_data *key_data)
44{
45 int i;
46 for(i = 0; i < *n_key_data; i++){
47 if(key_data[i].key_data_contents[0]){
48 memset(key_data[i].key_data_contents[0],
49 0,
50 key_data[i].key_data_length[0]);
51 free(key_data[i].key_data_contents[0]);
52 }
53 if(key_data[i].key_data_contents[1])
54 free(key_data[i].key_data_contents[1]);
55 }
56 *n_key_data = 0;
57}
58
59
60void
61kadm5_free_principal_ent(void *server_handle,
62 kadm5_principal_ent_t princ)
63{
64 kadm5_server_context *context = server_handle;
65
66 if (princ->principal)
67 krb5_free_principal(context->context, princ->principal);
68 if (princ->mod_name)
69 krb5_free_principal(context->context, princ->mod_name);
70 kadm5_free_key_data(server_handle, &princ->n_key_data, princ->key_data);
71 while (princ->n_tl_data && princ->tl_data) {
72 krb5_tl_data *tp;
73 tp = princ->tl_data;
74 princ->tl_data = tp->tl_data_next;
75 princ->n_tl_data--;
76 memset(tp->tl_data_contents, 0, tp->tl_data_length);
77 free(tp->tl_data_contents);
78 free(tp);
79 }
80 free(princ->key_data);
81 free(princ->policy);
82}
83
84void
85kadm5_free_name_list(void *server_handle,
86 char **names,
87 int *count)
88{
89 int i;
90 for(i = 0; i < *count; i++)
91 free(names[i]);
92 free(names);
93 *count = 0;
94}
